  <has_mechanism rdf:resource="#7d384d47e60f4d82abcd6db:PseudoAnonymization"/>
  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">845a9846c48f4fa38314800</uuid>
  <does rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean">true</does>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">3 WITH WHOM DO WE SHARE YOUR INFORMATION? Except as provided below we do not share or sell information that identifies our users personally or makes it possible for other parties to contact them directly We share your information as follows Other Users We may disclose personal information to other people who use our services if you choose to include personal information such as your email address photo or other details in your public profile Your username and location and any other information or content you post publicly will be shared with others when you use the public features of our services such as logging a geocache or participating in the discussion forums</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

